Simple HTTP server implemented on C
===================================

Use ``make server`` to build 

Implented methods: GET, POST

You can add static files to the static directory. 
They will be automatically processed and mapped to url paths

The formatted documentation also be read online at:

    https://apploidx.github.io/c-http-server/


